# Claude Settings for js-sdk-common

## Git Commit Behavior
- NEVER commit changes unless the user explicitly asks you to
- Do not automatically sign commits or use GPG signing
- Do not skip git hooks (--no-verify, --no-gpg-sign)

## Pull Request Descriptions
- PR descriptions should always be based on the GitHub PR template if one exists
- Do not automatically generate or modify PR descriptions unless explicitly requested
- If creating a PR description, always check for `.github/pull_request_template.md` or `.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md` first

## General Guidelines
- Only commit when explicitly asked by the user
- Respect all existing git workflows and configurations

